data.description: Beautiful 5 BR 3 BA home, with two of those bedrooms considered master bedrooms, located in Lynndale Subdivision that has been updated and renovated. Located in a well established subdivision and Brusly School District. Kitchen features 5-burner gas cooktop, 2 wall ovens, microwave and abundant cabinets. Refrigerator, washer, dryer to remain with the sale of the home. Great room features beautiful hearth surrounding large fireplace. Ceiling fans throughout the home. Walls have been freshly painted with beautiful color. Flooring-ceramic tile and luxury vinyl plank throughout home. Open patio area overlooking the above ground pool-so nice and relaxing. Home has rain gutters and the exterior has been freshly painted. Roof is 5 years old. Detached, aluminum, shed for extra storage. Backyard completely, wood, fenced with rail fence across the upper area of driveway. Off street parking for 4+ cars. Lovely landscaping in front of the home. Stress free commutes on the west side of the river. Conveniently located near commercial, retail businesses and restaurants. This is a home is a must see. Call for your showing today.
